Counter - Class in p.n.countbook
A counter is basic counting object which allows a name for an item, a count for an item (and its count on initialisation), as well as a comment for that item and the date for when these variables were initialized or changed to be associated.
Counter(String, int) - Constructor for class p.n.countbook.Counter
Initializes a count with just a name and a count (Set as the intital and current count), but with a blank comment.
Counter(String, int, String) - Constructor for class p.n.countbook.Counter
Initializes a count with just a name and a count (Set as the intital and current count), but with a user-defined comment.
